  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "See, but the only thing I was in this time in Siauliai, they made a ghetto for these people, because they didn't want to close up the factory.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because they wouldn't have expert trade people who can run the factory.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They made a special ghetto, and they didn't touch-- they killed a lot of people, you know, older people, and invalids, you know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But the only thing I was there between them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And most of them worked in this factory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But we had dates, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This and this date, they going to kill us, like in Panevezys, like in the other cities.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But they, they call us a commissioner from, from German government.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He was the, the rulers on this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "When he had an order they taking away the Jews to kill, he used to run away to Berlin.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he used to come in from Berlin with an order to stop it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because he used to say, if you kill the Jewish people, we have to close the factory.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They don't want to close the factory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It's very important for the German army to have this factory.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The leather factory.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Must be, everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, in this time is already there was war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They was allied for one year.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after a year, the German started war with Russia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no allied already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Russian was already enemies from Germany.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And Germany was-- they took over this before the Russian government had the factory-- Frankl's factory.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When he by himself, Frankl was in the United States.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think they took over Lithuania, I think was in, in summertime, I think in May or June.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We heard, even from Panevezys.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know right away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But after this, we fine-- we used to hear.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
